summary: Taylor Swift, Brie Larson, Lily James, or Jennifer Lawrence? I can’t decide.
question: Taylor Swift, Brie Larson, Lily James, or Jennifer Lawrence? I can’t decide.
answer:
Wow, those are tough choices, my dear!

Since I’m so very excited about Captain Marvel, I’d love to see Brie Larson around - but also Lily James, because I adore her and she’d have so many friends around? Taylor Swift and Jennifer Lawrence would have instant connections here as well… But I think, personally, I’m going to stick with Brie!

Hey, Royals, who would you love to see?

- Maria

summary: Brie Larson and John Cho to Receive Honorary Awards at the 2nd Annual LAOFCS Awards Ceremony on January 9th
title: Brie Larson and John Cho to Receive Honorary Awards at the 2nd Annual LAOFCS Awards Ceremony on January 9th
excerpt: The event will take place at the Taglyan Complex in Los Angeles
description: Brie Larson will be receiving their 2nd annual Trailblazer Award. In 2018, Jessica Chastain was the first recipient to receive the award. The Trailblazer Award was created to highlight and celebrate actors and filmmakers who not only speak out about important topics but are advocates for change.
